{"tid":826600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[山竹導致時空扭曲?】紅隧口驚現17年前(2001)賀歲片廣告","createTime":"2018-09-18T10:45:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T10:59:52.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e67419102e2a39e18e99c67c8224add8fc64db0e","tid":826600,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:45:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1876435/org/9dd2b1d7c4f7723b6c86745d2abc6b61.jpg/O4SUWtR-ugL6B_badBKLmV5FzVDed5mSkgp72JIKe9g?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1876435%2Forg%2F9dd2b1d7c4f7723b6c86745d2abc6b61.jpg%2FO4SUWtR-ugL6B_badBKLmV5FzVDed5mSkgp72JIKe9g%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=c28421b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1876507/org/9bbbec4571d5a29c4d75e221f7e76d71.JPG/7xthdcnJdl2VSZLxZJNik9R7WdFmx-Q9kOTd2pDk3do?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1876507%2Forg%2F9bbbec4571d5a29c4d75e221f7e76d71.JPG%2F7xthdcnJdl2VSZLxZJNik9R7WdFmx-Q9kOTd2pDk3do%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ec866321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n紅磡海底隧道口的廣告，新廣告被吹起後被逼「露底」，露出底版，然後驚現底版原來係2001年賀歲片《特務迷城》個廣告。到底有關方面係懶得換個廣告，定係唔捨得換呢個廣告呢？有網民就提供一個專業解說。<br />\n<br />\n大風吹之下，紅隧口驚現17年前，由成龍主演的賀歲片《特務迷城》廣告，在2018年的今日，坐車見到呢個舊廣告，真係別有一番風味，有網民話係咪電影的平行時空來到現實，更有人直指好似置身結界，非常有趣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/236871/%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%E5%B1%B1%E7%AB%B9-%E5%8D%81%E8%99%9F%E9%A2%A8%E7%90%83%E4%BB%A4%E7%B4%85%E9%9A%A7-%E9%9C%B2%E5%BA%95-%E5%9F%8B%E4%B8%8B17%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E8%B3%80%E6%AD%B2%E7%89%87%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%2F236871%2F%25E9%25A2%25B1%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%25AB%25B9-%25E5%258D%2581%25E8%2599%259F%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E7%25B4%2585%25E9%259A%25A7-%25E9%259C%25B2%25E5%25BA%2595-%25E5%259F%258B%25E4%25B8%258B17%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2589%258D%25E8%25B3%2580%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2589%2587%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589&d=qu2zEATov2gwXhtY4ibB6EkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=1a371cb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/236871/%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%E5%B1%B1%E7%AB%B9-%E5%8D%81%E8%99%9F%E9%A2%A8%E7%90%83%E4%BB%A4%E7%B4%85%E9%9A%A7-%E9%9C%B2%E5%BA%95-%E5%9F%8B%E4%B8%8B17%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E8%B3%80%E6%AD%B2%E7%89%87%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89</a>"},{"pid":"1cb19cde2ce2a73b67a6f936eb4cf26e48094ff2","tid":826600,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3135873a9e8551a1acfe6d0712bec526392db1","tid":826600,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:47:45.000Z","msg":"古董<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3fa65e2eb87feb5b4c663b01d84b92146b922ce","tid":826600,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:48:00.000Z","msg":"2001又有個玉免係10級, 風速150km/hr<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c92c209642d13923bab06fe90a60d97556ad638","tid":826600,"uid":25327,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:49:57.000Z","msg":"2001+17=2018<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c1f6165ddd767db8fe298f84ce38ccbc6fc34d","tid":826600,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:50:51.000Z","msg":"同考古一樣，再下層可能80年代"},{"pid"